{
  "stem": "16503.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 321.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, I'm sure there was a lot of talented people all locked up there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But it was a really-- it could go on Broadway.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I tell you that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It could.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was great.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "At least-- I am prejudiced, but it could.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I-- I feel that the old people and you know, that they had it very bad, and they couldn't-- you know, they died much sooner they would have.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But as I said-- and I'm going back to the same story-- if my family could have outlasted the war in Theresienstadt, we would have been a unit coming back with the old memories, bad ones, I'm sure, but then friendships like I had in, in, in a home with youngsters which are not most of them alive.",
      "word_count": 58
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was really un-- unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now my sister was considered a grownup, so she lived with my mother.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] she worked with her in a-- in a, well, a washing place.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What did I call it?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Laundry.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Laundry, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Thank you.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] boy, at one point-- I'm very sorry for that because at one point there was an offer from the Jewish community unit there.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, they've got books on all the-- all, all the how it was run and who was who.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I can't tell you.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I do not know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I know my sister is expert on it, but I am not, and I don't intend to be.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But you-- Jewish community offered my father but that he could get a room and the four of us could live in that room as a family in ghe-- in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my father was a very unusual man, and he knew that I was doing well in the children's home.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
